Fixes 8 issues found in audit:

- XSS: escapeHtml() added to phase.ts; used in handleHandoffConfirm in both
  phase-controls and phase-chip for project.name, briefing, and checklist items
- Async: handleHandoffConfirm now has try/catch/finally in both components;
  setAdvancing(false) guaranteed via finally even on failure
- Async: handoff-modal setSaving now in finally block (was only in catch)
- sidebar.tsx: useLocation() from react-router replaces window.location.pathname
  so Vault/Pipeline nav items are properly reactive to navigation
- sidebar.tsx: removed unused cn import
- vault/page.tsx: merged duplicate @plane/ui imports
- phase-badge.tsx: removed unused PHASE_ORDER import
- pipeline-board.tsx: logo_props typed as TLogoProps instead of unknown/any

